{"tid":1086371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱落老蘭 有條女叫我送佢番屋企","createTime":"2019-03-31T17:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T06:19:22.000Z","uid":212760,"like":96,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed5e9a14b9df75ffa9fb52a473dfe8a6abaa933","tid":1086371,"uid":212760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:28:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的 頭先落老蘭 諗住聽日放假 覓食一下<br />\n跟住去一間平時去開嘅bar<br />\n睇下有冇啲好樣啲嘅 嚟手就汁番件<br />\n但係話就話我放假姐 其他人都要番<br />\n所以就比較少人去 係到坐左成粒鐘都落唔到手<br />\n諗住死死氣番屋企自己黎就算<br />\n點知臨走落到門口個時<br />\n有條超額完成嘅女走埋黎搭我膊頭話佢啲fd走哂 <br />\n問我可唔可以送佢番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都講到咁 紋哂身 大家知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我就話  靚女咁夜咁危險 以後有咩事打我呢個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我講完呢句之黎 佢另埋一邊陰陰嘴笑<br />\n我心諗 估唔到學生時期溝女啲幽默感仲係咁得<br />\n當我舉手截的嘅時候 佢跑番去頭先間bar嘅門口<br />\n之後佢同成班人係到笑 然後就話 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">愚人節快樂[size=3]<br />\n我即刻小出聲 大叫：[size=5]好L好玩阿？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻沖上的士閃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df760269f8838338372632bb8ec24c024f6b3f8","tid":1086371,"uid":212760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1b6c563096a5fdec3e8a280e75fd9114fc545c","tid":1086371,"uid":201414,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />建議樓主屙督尿照下自己個樣先 有自信係好既 但係...毒撚最忌有自信<img src=\"/asse